CM_ SG_ 2566669054 TireLocation "Identifies which tire is associated with the parametric data in PGN 64578. Refer to SPN 929 for further details and examples. The low order 4 bits represent a position number, counting left to right when facing in the direction of normal vehicle ...";
CM_ SG_ 2566669054 TirePress "Pressure at which air is contained in cavity formed by tire and rim. See SPN 241 for alternate tire pressure with a lower range and coarser resolution.";
