CM_ BO_ 2564095742 "Data Security
The data security parameter group is used to send security entities of a given type and length. These entities are data produced by or used for applications of cryptography and supporting procedures to ensure data security.";
CM_ SG_ 2564095742 DataSecurityParameter "This Parameter is used to send the data for the Data Security message. There are presently four different items defined. The Data Security Parameter shall be sent least significant byte first.";
