CM_ BO_ 2560556798 "DTC Counts
The purpose of this DM is to identify the number of DTCs in each category. The categories are pending, all pending, MIL-on, previously MIL-on, and permanent DTCs.";
CM_ BO_ 2566750462 "Permanent DTCs
The purpose of this DM is to provide the list of permanent DTCs that are currently present. Permanent DTCs are defined as a confirmed or active MIL-on fault code that is currently commanding the MIL on and is stored in non-volatile ...";
